Package gui_principal

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApprovalTimeExtensionController
    The class contains the functionality of approving the extra time of an active exam that solve now by group of students.
    PrincipalController
    The class included in the diagrams and contains all the functionality that the principal has, manages the left menu in the system and describes the privileges that the principal has in the system.
    PrincipalDisplayReporByController
    The class is included in the diagrams and contains all the functionality available to the principal, for requesting various reports in the system.
    PrincipalDisplayReporByStudentController  
    PrincipalDisplayReportByTeacherController
    The class is included in the diagrams and contains all the functionality that the principal needs to do to see the requested report.
    PrincipalGetReportsController
    The class contains functionality for selecting a report type according to various parameters.
